FROM ubuntu:18.04

# Install build environment
RUN \
    apt-get update && \
    apt-get -y upgrade && \
    apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y build-essential wget python python-pip python3 libssl-dev libexpat-dev
# Create workspace
WORKDIR /WAFBench
COPY . /WAFBench
#  Install WAFBench
RUN \
    pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt && \
    make -C wb && make -C wb install && \
    ln -sf /WAFBench/pywb/main.py /bin/pywb && \
    chmod 744 /bin/pywb && \
    ln -sf /WAFBench/ftw_compatible_tool/main.py /bin/ftw_compatible_tool && \
    chmod 744 /bin/ftw_compatible_tool

#  Install Gunicorn
RUN apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y gunicorn
